                    <td>${a.scanId ? `<a href="#/results?id=${a.scanId}">#${a.scanId}</a>` : '—'}</td>
                </tr>`).join('')}</tbody>
            </table>`;
        } catch (e) {
            showToast('Failed to load audit log', 'error');
        }
    }

